Config - Annotation Interface in nusri.fyp.demo.annotation
This annotation is used to mark fields that should be configurable and serialized.
It allows the specification of a default value for the annotated field, which will be used
if the field's value is not set or is null.

Fields annotated with this annotation are processed by the ConfigService class.
